<emphasis bold="true" box="[1392,1568,3431,3464]" pageId="6" pageNumber="697">Distribution.</emphasis>
Loyalty Is (Lifou and Maré), 
<collectingCountry box="[1987,2203,3431,3464]" name="New Caledonia" pageId="6" pageNumber="697">New Caledonia</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
